thread.title: David Dainton
thread.title_full: Clubhouse Golf reviewed by David Dainton

author: David Dainton
title: David Dainton
text:
Ordered a 'Motocaddy M3 Pro Electric Golf Trolley 36 Hole Lithium Battery' on the Thursday with delivery UK Mainland 3 Days. Received an e-mail on Friday at 08:28 saying 'Your Clubhouse Golf order will be delivered today between 10:06-11:06' with the driver's name. It arrived at 10:15.
Excellent website, communications, delivery and overall service.
Strongly recommended.
